## Architecture

```
bitscrape/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ core/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ models.py       # Request, Response, BaseItem, CrawlStats (Pydantic)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ settings.py     # Settings (pydantic-settings, env-driven)
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ spider.py       # Base Spider class
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scheduler/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ scheduler.py    # MemoryQueue | RedisQueue + Scheduler
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ dupefilter.py   # Fingerprint-based deduplication
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ downloader/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ downloader.py   # aiohttp async downloader + retry + Playwright
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ parser/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ selector.py     # CSS/XPath via selectolax + ParsedResponse
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ middleware/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ middleware.py   # UserAgent, Robots, Cookie + MiddlewareManager
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ pipeline/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ pipelines.py    # BasePipeline, Logging, Validation, Dedup, Postgres
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ exporters/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ feed.py         # JSONL, JSON, CSV, XML exporters
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ workflow/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ graph.py        # LangGraph state machine (fetch‚Üíparse‚Üípipeline)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cli/
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ main.py         # Click CLI: crawl, startproject, genspider, list
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ engine.py           # Central Engine ‚Äî orchestrates everything
```

### Crawl flow

```
start_urls
    ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº
[Scheduler] ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îê
    ‚îÇ  next_request()                                  ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº                                                  ‚îÇ
[Middleware.process_request]                           ‚îÇ
    ‚îÇ                                                  ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº                                                  ‚îÇ
[Downloader.fetch]  ‚óÑ‚îÄ‚îÄ Playwright (use_playwright=True) ‚îÇ
    ‚îÇ                                                  ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº                                                  ‚îÇ
[Middleware.process_response]                          ‚îÇ
    ‚îÇ                                                  ‚îÇ
    ‚ñº                                                  ‚îÇ
[Spider.parse(ParsedResponse)]                         ‚îÇ
    ‚îÇ                                                  ‚îÇ
    ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ yield Request ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îò
    ‚îÇ
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ yield Item
            ‚îÇ
            ‚ñº
      [PipelineManager]
            ‚îÇ
            ‚ñº
       [FeedExporter]  ‚Üí file / stdout
            ‚îÇ
            ‚ñº
       [Postgres/Supabase]  (PostgresPipeline)
```

---

## Settings reference

All settings can be overridden via environment variables prefixed `BITSCRAPE_`:

| Setting | Default | Env var |
|---|---|---|
| `concurrent_requests` | 16 | `BITSCRAPE_CONCURRENT_REQUESTS` |
| `download_delay` | 0.0 | `BITSCRAPE_DOWNLOAD_DELAY` |
| `download_timeout` | 30 | `BITSCRAPE_DOWNLOAD_TIMEOUT` |
| `scheduler_use_redis` | false | `BITSCRAPE_SCHEDULER_USE_REDIS` |
| `redis_url` | redis://localhost:6379/0 | `BITSCRAPE_REDIS_URL` |
| `database_url` | None | `BITSCRAPE_DATABASE_URL` |
| `robotstxt_obey` | true | `BITSCRAPE_ROBOTSTXT_OBEY` |
| `max_depth` | None | `BITSCRAPE_MAX_DEPTH` |
| `feed_uri` | None | `BITSCRAPE_FEED_URI` |
| `feed_format` | jsonl | `BITSCRAPE_FEED_FORMAT` |

---

## Distributed mode (Redis)

```bash
export BITSCRAPE_SCHEDULER_USE_REDIS=true
export BITSCRAPE_REDIS_URL=redis://redis-host:6379/0

# Start multiple workers ‚Äî they all share the queue
bitscrape crawl myspider.py &
bitscrape crawl myspider.py &
bitscrape crawl myspider.py &
```

---

## JavaScript rendering (Playwright)

```python
class JSSpider(Spider):
    name = "js"
    start_urls = ["https://spa-example.com/"]

    async def parse(self, response: ParsedResponse):
        # response.body already contains fully rendered HTML
        yield {"title": response.css("h1::text").get()}

# Mark requests for Playwright:
yield self.follow("/dynamic-page", use_playwright=True)
```

